commit_list.message:
remove statement from early_posting in Apex JSON

Instead of

    "early_article_posting": {
        "consent": true,
        "statement": "Yes, I agree to publish an early version of my article"
    },

it'll become

    "early_article_posting": {
        "consent": true,
    },

